### 브랜드 기능
### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 1) 브랜드 캠페인 목록 조회
### GET /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 2. 캠페인 생성
### POST /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/create/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
POST https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/create/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "내추라펫 저알러지 닭고기 사료",
  "product_image_url": "https://cdn.pawfecto.kr/products/naturapet_chicken.png",
  "product_description": "요구조건(requirements)을 포함한 캠페인 등록 테스트입니다. 저알러지 성견용 사료입니다.",
  "target_pet_type": "dog",
  "min_follower_count": 5000,
  "required_creator_count": 2,
  "requested_at": "2025-02-01T09:00:00Z",
  "application_deadline_at": "2025-02-10",
  "posting_start_at": "2025-02-15",
  "posting_end_at": "2025-02-28",
  "style_tag_ids": [1, 3],
  "requirements": [
    {
      "requirement_type": "object",
      "description": "사료 패키지가 명확히 보이도록 촬영",
      "is_required": true
    },
    {
      "requirement_type": "text",
      "description": "급여 후 반응을 캡션에 작성",
      "is_required": true
    }
  ]
}




### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 3) 캠페인 상세 조회 (요구조건 포함)
### GET /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 4) 캠페인 수정 (요구조건까지 한 번에 수정)
### PUT /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/update/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PUT https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/update/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "min_follower_count": 8000,
  "requirements": [
    {
      "requirement_type": "scene",
      "description": "실내 거실에서 반려견과 함께 촬영",
      "is_required": true
    }
  ]
}



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 5. 포스팅 요구조건 목록 조회
### GET /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/requirements/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/requirements/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 6. 포스팅 요구조건 생성 (추가)
### POST /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/requirements/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
POST https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/requirements/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requirement_type": "action",
  "description": "사료를 급여하는 장면 포함",
  "is_required": false
}



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 7. 포스팅 요구조건 수정
### PATCH /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/requirements/{requirement_id}/update/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PATCH https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/requirements/3/update/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "사료를 급여하고 반응이 보이도록 촬영"
}



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 8. 포스팅 요구조건 삭제
### DELETE /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/requirements/{requirement_id}/delete/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
DELETE https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/requirements/3/delete/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 캠페인 삭제
### DELETE /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/delete/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
DELETE https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/21/delete/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

