### [브랜드] Campaign 진행 관련
### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 1) 브랜드 입장에서 특정 캠페인에 대한 크리에이터 목록 조회 (브랜드)
###    (creator recommendations)
### GET /api//v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/acceptances/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/acceptances/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 2) 브랜드가 크리에이터 승인
### PATCH /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/acceptances/{acceptance_id}/approve/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PATCH https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/acceptances/21/approve/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ㄴ> 400 Bad Request 테스트 완료 : "이미 승인 또는 거절된 크리에이터입니다."



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 3) 브랜드가 크리에이터 거절
### PATCH /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/acceptances/{acceptance_id}/reject/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PATCH https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/20/acceptances/22/reject/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ㄴ> 400 Bad Request 테스트 완료 : "이미 승인 또는 거절된 크리에이터입니다."



